{"id": "1462325902355599481", "channel_id": "1326453763355185215", "author_id": "229363452026552323", "author_name": "anikid9000", "content": "Like, the limited dialogue from Xu that we have atm fits with Xura being this contrasted location of Unattained Pleasures, quite literally. The mofit of something that appears pleasant and beautiful masking something horrific is there in Xura, the Yellow robed figure, and Xu. There's also the mail from a few months ago, apparently from a Dreamless Land resident, specifically mentioning having their hands cleansed and perfumed, fitting with how Xura's hidden decay is described", "timestamp": "2026-01-18T06:01:03.823000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-01-18T06:01:53.729000+00:00", "attachments": [{"id": "1462325901692764190", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 16900, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1326453763355185215/1462325901692764190/image.png?ex=6a34db1f&is=6a33899f&hm=08292e3134405a6f9d3d4f833c1335ee26f7ed9346f71e4ef36b9583225e9dfa&"}, {"id": "1462325902099878091", "filename": "Android_Device_1_16_2026_10_17_38_PM.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1014823, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1326453763355185215/1462325902099878091/Android_Device_1_16_2026_10_17_38_PM.png?ex=6a34db1f&is=6a33899f&hm=1d3a6f6c8de0e32503fa7019adca1e50eb0c0d117ab1455626cfd9c6c1698cbc&"}]}
